Check Splitters
===============

A web app for splitting shared expenses across a group.


Requirements
------------

Node.js  22+
npm      10+


Dependencies
------------

Server
  express         4.18
  better-sqlite3  9.4
  cors            2.8
  uuid            9.0

Client
  react           19
  react-dom       19
  react-router-dom  7
  vite            8


Setup
-----

Install dependencies for the server and client:

  cd server && npm install
  cd ../client && npm install


Running locally
---------------

Start the server (runs on port 3001):

  cd server
  npm start

Start the client in a separate terminal (runs on port 5173):

  cd client
  npm run dev

Open http://localhost:5173 in your browser.


Testing with multiple users
---------------------------

To simulate multiple users on the same machine, use separate browser contexts
that do not share localStorage:

  - Regular window (user 1)
  - Incognito window (user 2)
  - A different browser entirely (user 3)

Create a session in one window, then join using the 6-digit invite code
in the others.
